### Test Auth API - Dang Nhap va Dang Ky

@baseUrl = https://localhost:7047
@contentType = application/json

### 1. Dang Ky Tai Khoan Moi
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "email": "user123@example.com",
    "matKhau": "password123"
}

### 2. Dang Nhap
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "email": "user123@example.com",
    "matKhau": "password123"
}

### 3. Dang Nhap That Bai (sai mat khau)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "email": "user123@example.com",
    "matKhau": "sai"
}

### 4. Dang Ky Email Trung
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "email": "user123@example.com",
    "matKhau": "password456"
}
